VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \b(strcpy|strcat|sprintf|gets)\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:strlcpy|snprintf|strncpy|vTaskStacks|configMAX_TASK_NAME_LEN
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects unsafe string APIs common in memory-corruption vulnerabilities.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Freertos Unsafe String Copy API.
